Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The night I returned home from the Awa dance festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still hadn't collected my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:15.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For a moment, my consciousness had rewound to the day after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:20.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It felt as if the world I'd been living in until now was a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:22.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd just woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As if the person I am now was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:32.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Could... my memory be returning?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will my current self disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:39.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will I have to start over from the day after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:45.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens... my current consciousness, my current mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,will disappear soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:51.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Without anyone knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:56.01,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(296,297)}I'll Be Back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Before I can even say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:01:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if we could meet in a dream, could I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:30.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if sadness alone floats down from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:38.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that kind of voice pains you even now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:42.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if, off to the side, our hands are placed on each other's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This memory wouldn't fade, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:54.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if, when our eyes meet, I can't say the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:58.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your words illuminate the world more than anyone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:02.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Next to me, "Goodbye means I love you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be forthright
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Though I alone sing of loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you means I'm in love with you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The world's end of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're not allowed in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the committee officer who lent us our costumes said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because we messed up yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:41.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We stopped dancing and put a damper on the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:44.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us clearly hadn't practiced enough, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:50.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They said they couldn't continue dealing with the Fukurai University festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The other groups apparently agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:54.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were sick. You couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we had practiced more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:10.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, if the other groups won't help us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,does that mean we won't be able to borrow costumes or music?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What about next month's school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But we practiced so hard for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But without costumes or music...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what we should do, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:32.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but if we don't do anything at all, it'll mean the end of the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start by doing whatever we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:41.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is no good, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't sort your garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it later. Just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Running?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I was thinking of starting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, apparently, I was in the track club in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the festival club's in trouble because of me, and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:14.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be able to sleep if I got some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there some other reason you can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:21.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're about to run off somewhere at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:39.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:40.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:41.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:55.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Before I know it, maybe no one will know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:58.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Without anyone realizing it, maybe I'll just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I keep having these scary thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:09.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't told Yana-san or anyone else about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:13.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, is that what you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That you haven't told everyone about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried that Miss Ultrasonic doesn't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and that you'll affect Mitsuo's relationship with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to sleep because I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:34.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere for me to run... and I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make everything fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm Kaga Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you could even conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It scares me that I feel like I really could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:18.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you want to come to my place tonight for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,B-e-e-f is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:30.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Kouko right here has...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I received a huge chunk of Kobe beef as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kobe beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If they listen while eating delicious food,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,they can keep calm, no matter how serious the discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then. Mitsuo's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've got class soon, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Volunteer work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:17.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,An upperclassman in the film club asked me to gather dried leaves for a shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I meant to ask if you wanted to come eat at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:27.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a bag to put these in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:46.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This was yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gathering leaves, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping Yana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather them together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:01.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered these leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They have nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:11.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd do anything so ill-natured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:14.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've known for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've been like this ever since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:24.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to associate with people who do things behind Yana's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just hear me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Over beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen while eating beef at my place tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beef?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I really want you to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko's bringing Kobe beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to miss that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't want to associate with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm avoiding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're clearly avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:50.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...it was a mistake to cut my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... W-well, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one else is here yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:26.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There might be something I want to tell you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you before everyone else came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I meant to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on your way to Banri's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's super suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You want something with my guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:05.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I just came to hang out with Banri's neighbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:09.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,With this girl here. This is Nana-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk, I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:24.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai was really worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:28.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I jumped to conclusions and tried to pick a fight with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:37.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The other night, when I saw you being friendly with Linda-senpai on campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,do you know what I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That I was having an affair with the girl Yana-san loves-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:45.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, "Yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"All right! Lucky me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Now Yana will be rejected!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"And then I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"I can..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:03.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I like Yana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:12.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it the moment I learned\NYana was in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's stupid, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I actually didn't want anyone else to have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended not to be interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but it was because I thought Yana would like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got complacent fighting imaginary enemies, and got stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:36.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The world was chugging along, tens of thousands of light years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:43.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I pretended I didn't really care, and cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:50.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After cutting it off, my appearance suddenly changed so much, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:12:01.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand why I was so hurt that I'd cut off the hair I'd kept long for years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And I really, really regretted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:15.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But instead of blaming myself, I lashed out at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know I made you feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will you film my face right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:43.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep a record of how stupid I'm being right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:44.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been wanting to tell you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to wait until everyone got here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri... It's Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:34.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But Banri keeps asking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:49.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call Kouko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you rather go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:00.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in college now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a year and a half since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm dating Kouko now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:17.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I left, Kouko would be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She'd cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:19.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:24.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:24.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't tell her about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:30.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Kouko my memories returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what you do to someone who's lost his senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:51.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... Don't tell Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:52.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live with Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to pretend it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So don't tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:13.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:17.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my turn now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear like he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forget everything that happened in the past year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be like everything I did with\NKouko never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Target found!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, you overdid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:21.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But you told me to cut him off and catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's sit down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:39.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I wanted to tell you guys today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking for a while that I needed to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I just couldn't bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to think I was a liar, or that I didn't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought up all kinds of reasons not to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But really, it's not any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell you because I was afraid to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,how truly deep, wide, and permanent the damage was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:11.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any sense, does it? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:16.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! It's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not as though we had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:24.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned a lot of things at the cult's overnight trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not easy for you to say, don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just skip over it for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:41.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably the same as dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:47.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I came back to life and made it this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:51.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing is going right anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared, I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I tried running, but all I learned was that I couldn't run from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:05.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, what are you afraid will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:13.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid... that I'll disappear without anyone noticing, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "disappear"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I disappear now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:21.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone would be able to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:29.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But let's do something about it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to it, we'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll really disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and honestly, I don't really understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but if that's how you say it is, we have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you've got Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:59.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you go, she'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:04.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,While screaming, "Banri, where are you?! I love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:22.52,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(559,47)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Kaga Koko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:22.52,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(521,79)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}No subject{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:18.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ultrasonic told me not to ask, so I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:21.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We ate all the beef together next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:30.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You told me not to tell Kaga-san, so I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After that, Kaga-san brought the beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I just told her you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What'd Kouko say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"I see. He ran away?" That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:54.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I want you to film what\NI'm about to say with the Okamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:55.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to leave a record of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that I was here, and alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:07.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want our future selves to know that I lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:13.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to leave a mark... so that I won't lose my old self again when I look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:26.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:35.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much time I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:39.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In the next moment, I might disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I may stay the way I am for ten or fifty more years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't do any good to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do what I can, while I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the light that will help me find Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:03.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose my way... with this light,\NI know I can return to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:07.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we meet again, I'm sure our love will come back to life again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want her to trust me and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many or which paths I take,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I will always return to her in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was going to tell Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:24.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:29.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't promise a future with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:35.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't said anything until now, but I think this is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:41.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I only came to college to follow Mitsuo, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:45.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was always my plan, from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:46.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:15.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, I'm telling you you're wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you still don't notice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:24.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Though I've wanted to touch that arm for the past two or three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The urge to scream is so great that, look, I can't stand it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:44.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So why, why won't you notice even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really, really in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:57.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need words of flattery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Love me semi-eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After 5,000 years or so, I won't be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:07.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not endless
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I will die someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:17.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being told "I'll love you forever" won't make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, think only that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:25.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll love me till I die
