Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:29.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(299,371)}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:33.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(163,335)}Kouko, right now, you're the most
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:33.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(197,370)}awesome you've ever been!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.31,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(331,367)}Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.31,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(331,332)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:37.51,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(299,370)}Beef, woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.78,0:23:39.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Didn't we miss our chance to eat Kobe beef?
